{"tid":403323,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Live行山撚 日本表銀坐縱走 + 槍穗連峰縱走","createTime":"2017-09-17T06:18:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T02:47:17.000Z","uid":129364,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0fddf9ddce98f55edb79fd205285c8481f90688a","tid":403323,"uid":129364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T06:18:07.000Z","msg":"表銀坐縱走係講緊由燕岳到槍岳山莊既一段行山路線, 而槍穗連峰縱走就係由槍岳到穗高岳既一段路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔知各位有冇去過上高地, 槍穗連峰就係講緊上高地望上去果一堆山岳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今次我會由中房溫泉出發, 經燕岳, 大天井岳, 槍岳, 北穗高岳, 涸沢岳, 奧穗高岳, 最後返到去槍見館浸個靚溫泉做個結尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一共會係山上住4晚, 由於山上有時收唔到所以會不定期更新, 各位巴打支持下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b963c3aa72e23175c639aa27bcb94bcd180839a","tid":403323,"uid":19738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T06:27:23.000Z","msg":"樓主加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da6d61c895c1bcd5543f0966211df3454cdc67ed","tid":403323,"uid":129364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T06:34:01.000Z","msg":"飛機, jr , 巴士, 加加埋埋成十鳩幾個鍾, 終於到左起步點, 中房溫泉, 呢個中房溫泉係日本秘湯温泉協會認可既秘湯之一 , 呢個秘會要認你做秘湯第一件事就係個溫泉交通較唔方便, 呢間野係呢方面絕到係做到滿分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後就係講泉水質數, 要做到真係泉水源直你接引入, 唔溝水, 呢d先係真溫泉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢張圖就係2005年認可既158間秘湯啦, 有冇巴打去過邊間可以討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/17/143355_93a81d171453d5b73e5c50743dabcb31.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F17%2F143355_93a81d171453d5b73e5c50743dabcb31.jpg&h=9883776c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f698f654967af269e0839425ab493a438c10e8aa","tid":403323,"uid":129364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T06:43:10.000Z","msg":"今朝入中房全車得我一人, 唔知係咪泰利影響下冇咩人登山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/17/143914_e10ab8236327981b90557054da05a312.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F17%2F143914_e10ab8236327981b90557054da05a312.jpg&h=e5885c8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中房溫泉間房, 都幾殘舊, 多謝10000羊一晚<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/17/143937_acd5d6b0d6e3a0bb8f00255fe99ea35d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F17%2F143937_acd5d6b0d6e3a0bb8f00255fe99ea35d.jpg&h=c5761099&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7ddd652cf7df7cba28b41c42ad8f03267f8e7938","tid":403323,"uid":96779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0fddf9ddce98f55edb79fd205285c8481f90688a","tid":403323,"uid":129364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T06:18:07.000Z","msg":"表銀坐縱走係講緊由燕岳到槍岳山莊既一段行山路線, 而槍穗連峰縱走就係由槍岳到穗高岳既一段路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔知各位有冇去過上高地, 槍穗連峰就係講緊上高地望上去果一堆山岳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今次我會由中房溫泉出發, 經燕岳, 大天井岳, 槍岳, 北穗高岳, 涸沢岳, 奧穗高岳, 最後返到去槍見館浸個靚溫泉做個結尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一共會係山上住4晚, 由於山上有時收唔到所以會不定期更新, 各位巴打支持下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T02:47:17.000Z","msg":"ching 我打算十月頭去槍岳, 可唔可以留tg想請教下你<img src=\"/a